WA_Analysis

This script will graph and analyze all of the Washington data.

  1. Load in data and packages
  2. Manipulate data
  3. Graph
  1. Dev rate vs. dev temp - hatch to pupa
  2. Dev rate vs. dev temp - pupa to eclos (blocks 1+2 and pupa)
  3. Survival vs. dev temp - hatch to pupa (split by block, block 1+2)
  4. Survival vs. dev temp - pupa to eclos (just pupa data)
  5. Survival vs. dev temp - pupa to eclos (block 1+2 data) - lowest priority
  6. Pupal mass vs. dev temp (split by block, block 1+2 data only)
  1. Subsequent analyses as needed
